elements.name: Como usuario, quiero crear una nueva etiqueta, y si no me gusta eliminarla.

steps.name: I enter tag name "Nueva Etiqueta eliminar"
I enter tag description "Descripción de la nueva etiqueta"
I verify that an element tag with text "Nueva Etiqueta eliminar" exists
I click on tag with name "Nueva Etiqueta eliminar"
I verify that an header with text "Are you sure you want to delete this tag?" exists
I verify that an element tag with text "Nueva Etiqueta eliminar" does not exist
